### 4. Post a Balanced Entry
@bookId=book1
POST {{api}}/books/{{bookId}}/entries
content-type: application/json

{
  "memo": "Sale #1",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "lines": [
    { "accountCode": "1000", "debit": 1599 },
