}

### 5. List Entries for current month
GET {{api}}/books/{{bookId}}/entries?month=2025-08

### 6. Ledger for account 1000
GET {{api}}/books/{{bookId}}/accounts/1000/ledger?month=2025-08

### 7. Trial Balance (if endpoint exists)
GET {{api}}/books/{{bookId}}/reports/trial-balance?to=2025-08-31